# RouteLive uses Firebase (Auth + Firestore) with its public web config,
# which is committed to firebase-applet-config.json and safe for the
# client bundle (secured by Firestore rules).
#
# No client-side env vars are required for production.
#
# For Cloudflare Pages CI deploys, set these in your Cloudflare/Pages project
# secrets instead of this file:
#   CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID
#   CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN
